data.description: PRICED TO SELL! This gorgeous property is located in the well-known Walden on Lake Houston golf community. The spacious 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home with a pool has all you need and more! It's loaded with both formals, family room, breakfast room, game room and bonus room! No carpet downstairs! The primary is downstairs, and all other bedrooms are up. The upstairs split design showcases large additional bedrooms with privacy and access to two bathrooms. Let your imagination run wild upstairs with two spaces for entertaining, leisure or work. The open concept kitchen has plenty of counterspace and cabinets. Walk out in the back yard to the covered patio, private pool and green space. Recent updates include garage doors 2023, re-plastered pool 2023, roof 2019, water heater 2018, French drains 2018 and pool pump & motor 2017.
